{"tid":2107952,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"跪求介紹法科/薩滿等師傅,想先試唔洗食/聞奇怪嘢嘅師傅先.不能上學/班,病齡8年,腹瀉,手腳無力,25歲胖男","createTime":"2020-07-14T08:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T03:24:43.000Z","uid":46752,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8699fd69a5037abdddafa3b07cecb8b5dd9e364d","tid":2107952,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:13:32.000Z","msg":"不能上學/班，病齡8年，腹瀉，手腳無力，25歲胖男<br />\n<br />\n主訴：<br />\n我的蛋白質類攝取中只選極低脂的食物，如雞胸、極低脂魚柳、蝦。如食物中脂肪比例增加，如生牛肉湯濛（營養師建議吃），吃了有機會肚痛/腹瀉/&ldquo;濟&rdquo;/大便爛（以往出現，現在不敢吃，不確定）。<br />\n<br />\n現史：<br />\n手腳無力至僅能勉強自理（程度：煮一人餐都好辛苦），職業治療師診斷我手做重複性動作會累<br />\n手指耐力低<br />\n曾吃粗糧，肚臍上9cm位置頂<br />\n曾吃冷物，會覺得肚很冷<br />\n手腳掌出汗，手腳掌冰冷，腳板脫皮<br />\n小便分差，陽痿（連皮/剝皮香蕉硬度）<br />\n<br />\n往史:<br />\n09年9月-11年5月，曾常吃龜苓膏、飲涼茶，以防暗瘡，現回頭看不應吃。有手淫習慣<br />\n12年9月開始手腳無力至今<br />\n14年5月開始嚴重<br />\n6,7月很疲勞仍勉強上學/班，結果更疲勞<br />\n9月起經常腹瀉<br />\n<br />\n西醫:<br />\n精神科開了aripiprazole 5mg sertraline (hcl) 50mg 每日各半粒，藥後肚頂，待覆診<br />\n腦神經內科做了神經傳導檢查，排除了重症肌無力，問他有甚麼其他檢查可做，他說無。<br />\n內分泌科排除了Cushing's syndrome。<br />\n照過胸背頸x光。 <br />\n14年驗出肝酵素高。 <br />\n17年照胃鏡，有胃炎。 脂肪肝。<br />\n運動後更疲勞<br />\n<br />\n順勢療法：sulphur q1，沒改善<br />\n<br />\n中醫：<br />\n基本上以以下路線醫好一半，-代表藥後反應<br />\n參苓白朮散-止瀉、有力＞平胃散-大便變完整＞右歸丸贊育丹減約半熟地-吃油少少較不易肚屙＞便秘之後就睇黃志忠-好亂手寫個張＞十全大補-有力<br />\n另外：<br />\n補中益氣湯-有力<br />\n<br />\n病人資料、問診單、舊中藥、順勢處方：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffolderview%3Fid%3D1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=7b2e5e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/folderview?id=1w43NYFeh1boJcW3eXLO3aYg490VHeOjU</a><br />\n<br />\n無：食物敏感<br />\n<br />\n家人病歷：<br />\n父：痔瘡<br />\n母：乙型肝炎、小腸氣、割掉口水線有粒嘢<br />\n兄：無<br />\n<br />\ntg group/ tg(最活躍平台):<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=fbe674f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E38pyFcoqheNbzSaruFL-Q</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Usernamennn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FUsernamennn&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=1f5b9aac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Usernamennn</a><br />\n<br />\nfb page/ messager:<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/%E8%B7%AA%E6%B1%82%E7%A5%9E%E9%86%AB%E7%97%85%E9%BD%A18%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%9B%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD25%E6%AD%B2%E8%83%96%E7%94%B7-100320258254152/?ref=bookmarks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%25E8%25B7%25AA%25E6%25B1%2582%25E7%25A5%259E%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%25BD%25A18%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%2585%25B3%25E7%2584%25A1%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%2587%25B3%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%258F%25AD25%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E8%2583%2596%25E7%2594%25B7-100320258254152%2F%3Fref%3Dbookmarks&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=533d38ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/%E8%B7%AA%E6%B1%82%E7%A5%9E%E9%86%AB%E7%97%85%E9%BD%A18%E5%B9%B4%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E7%84%A1%E5%8A%9B%E8%87%B3%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E4%B8%8A%E5%AD%B8%E7%8F%AD25%E6%AD%B2%E8%83%96%E7%94%B7-100320258254152/?ref=bookmarks</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.me%2Fseek.chinesemedicine.1&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=f8ff0961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.me/seek.chinesemedicine.1</a><br />\n<br />\n跪求介紹治療師<br />\n請問他的療法有沒紀錄<br />\n1.醫好過我的主訴？<br />\n2.醫好過手腳無力及不能自理（程度不能煮一人餐）？<br />\n3.醫好過甚麼棘手個案<br />\n4.介不介意分享你甚麼病<br />\n5.你病了多長時間才醫好？<br />\n<br />\n待辦診治：CT了腦，等報告<br />\n髗骶骨療法<br />\n音叉<br />\n接地氣<br />\n薩滿<br />\n心理學家<br />\n吳神父按摩<br />\n<br />\n不知如何找：醫療靈媒<br />\n<br />\n未試，不覺得有用/未有實例吸引我：原始點<br />\n文王殿<br />\n芽山"},{"pid":"e1590896b211afe15334a1232335b51d9f8c4198","tid":2107952,"uid":361784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:55:45.000Z","msg":"Wow有個好似幾勁<br />\n你要幾多lv?"},{"pid":"eb389392c178dc5360cd1f7a25964e2f541ba82a","tid":2107952,"uid":100016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87f6f61e36fb704816b97d8e3ce95caa1b0ee6e0","tid":2107952,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T09:18:14.000Z","msg":"試下龍哥"},{"pid":"eaed7f60cfa8c83bb68777d2c2ed4a41becf5f99","tid":2107952,"uid":196697,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:04:39.000Z","msg":"精神病"},{"pid":"aaff463d1d47a0f31cf1d08e6c631473d4f2c10e","tid":2107952,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:34:16.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"c539fb84ef71c930e96c172f4d7c9d27518d2d0e","tid":2107952,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1590896b211afe15334a1232335b51d9f8c4198","tid":2107952,"uid":361784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:55:45.000Z","msg":"Wow有個好似幾勁<br />\n你要幾多lv?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"999"},{"pid":"8bc5f691c230e1073f162ad2a9069d5b3955d310","tid":2107952,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1590896b211afe15334a1232335b51d9f8c4198","tid":2107952,"uid":361784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T08:55:45.000Z","msg":"Wow有個好似幾勁<br />\n你要幾多lv?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T15:37:48.000Z","msg":"999"},{"pid":"8d48134dbdd2c3190b0942a4ab9787306df6e669","tid":2107952,"uid":223233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"搵潘兆聰"},{"pid":"40265166f231868b488931e104be11ccd603f7d6","tid":2107952,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8d48134dbdd2c319